    <h2 class="c-entry-box--compact__title"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="feature" href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/11/19/20961811/taliban-afghanistan-radio-in-a-box-djs-news-war-us-army">The Afghan DJs hired and abandoned by the US military</a></h2>
    
      <p class="p-dek c-entry-box--compact__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">They were hired to help with the war effort—and when the American military pulled out, those voices were left for dead</p>
    
    
    
      
        <div class="c-byline" data-cid="site/byline-1587441841_4005_124867" data-cdata='{"timestamp":1574172000}'>
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
        By
        <span class="c-byline__item">
          
            
            <a href="https://www.theverge.com/users/ChristopherHarland-Dunaway" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Christopher Harland-Dunaway</span></a>
          
        </span>
      
      
      <span class="c-byline__item">
        
